commit.message:
Set the "allowsInlineMediaPlayback" property on the WKWebView configuration to true to prevent video textures from automatically going full-screen.
Also changed default interface orientation to landscape-right, which fixes an issue where mouse event x-coordinates are inverted in the WKWebView.
